@dingoConfig_HostAddress = http://localhost:5089

# Milestone 1: Device Catalog Management API Tests

### Get catalog loading status
GET {{dingoConfig_HostAddress}}/api/catalogs/status
Accept: application/json

### Get all available catalogs
GET {{dingoConfig_HostAddress}}/api/catalogs
Accept: application/json

### Get available device types
GET {{dingoConfig_HostAddress}}/api/catalogs/types
Accept: application/json

### Get specific catalog - DingoPdm
GET {{dingoConfig_HostAddress}}/api/catalogs/DingoPdm
Accept: application/json

### Get non-existent catalog (should return 404)
GET {{dingoConfig_HostAddress}}/api/catalogs/NonExistentDevice
Accept: application/json

### Validate catalog by file path
POST {{dingoConfig_HostAddress}}/api/catalogs/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filePath": "../catalogs/ExampleDevice.json"
}

### Validate catalog by JSON content - Valid catalog
POST {{dingoConfig_HostAddress}}/api/catalogs/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "catalogJson": "{\n  \"deviceType\": \"TestDevice\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"manufacturer\": \"Test Manufacturer\",\n  \"description\": \"Test device\",\n  \"communication\": {\n    \"type\": \"CAN\",\n    \"baseId\": \"0x600\",\n    \"extendedFrames\": true\n  },\n  \"parameters\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"testParam\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Test Parameter\",\n      \"type\": \"uint16\",\n      \"address\": \"0x601\",\n      \"subIndex\": 1,\n      \"byteOrder\": \"littleEndian\",\n      \"defaultValue\": 100,\n      \"category\": \"Test\",\n      \"description\": \"Test parameter\",\n      \"isReadOnly\": false\n    }\n  ],\n  \"cyclicData\": []\n}"
}

### Validate catalog by JSON content - Invalid catalog (missing required fields)
POST {{dingoConfig_HostAddress}}/api/catalogs/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "catalogJson": "{\n  \"deviceType\": \"\",\n  \"version\": \"\",\n  \"communication\": {\n    \"type\": \"INVALID_TYPE\"\n  },\n  \"parameters\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"\",\n      \"type\": \"invalid_type\",\n      \"address\": \"invalid_address\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
}

### Validate catalog - Missing request body (should return 400)
POST {{dingoConfig_HostAddress}}/api/catalogs/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
}

### Test OpenAPI/Swagger documentation
GET {{dingoConfig_HostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

